title: Beautiful One Bedroom in the Heart of the Hill!
posting_body: ['Excelsior', '1535 Bellevue Ave, Seattle, WA, 98122', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 84', 'OR Text', '84', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'XCELLENT APARTMENTS ON CAPITOL HILL', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 611 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome home to Excelsior Seattle - modern apartments on Capitol Hill.', 'Amenities include sky lounge, roof deck, fitness center, parking garage, dog wash, bike storage and courtyard.', 'Excelsior offers a mixture of comfort, style, and convenience.', 'Features', '- Noise', 'Reducing Oversized Windows', '- Balconies*', '- Stainless Steel Appliance Package', '- Large patios*', '- Front loading washer/dryers', '- Weathered concrete looking flooring', '*Select homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Studio, 1 and 2 bedroom homes', '- Rooftop Deck', '- White Marble Countertops', '- Custom Cabinetry', '- Resident Lounge', '- Two Story Fitness Center', '- Dog Wash', '- Conference Room', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome up to 2 pets per apartment home.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'No weight limit.', 'Please call our leasing office for complete pet policy.', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'l8q3bHNhYjS']
